.SH NAME
drm_atomic_helper_bridge_duplicate_state \- Duplicate a bridge state object
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "struct drm_bridge_state *" drm_atomic_helper_bridge_duplicate_state
.BI "(struct drm_bridge *bridge "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "bridge" 12
bridge object
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Allocates a new bridge state and initializes it with the current bridge
state values. This helper is meant to be used as a bridge
\fIdrm_bridge_funcs.atomic_duplicate_state\fP hook for bridges that don't
subclass the bridge state.
